title: Family Support Specialist Interview
Application Type: I interviewed at Family and Childrens Services (Tulsa, OK)
Interview Descriptions: The interview process was quick and easy. Interviewer was friendly and did not make it seem like an interview. HR was prompt about asking for next steps in the hiring process. They called within an hour after the interview
Interview Questions: How did you find out about us?

title: Registered Nurse Interview
Application Type: I applied online. The process took 2 days. I interviewed at Family and Childrens Services (Tulsa, OK) in Apr 2021
Interview Descriptions: Interview was conducted via Zoom. Interviewers were very courteous and time-conscientious. They were  very organized with interview questions and skilled at keeping me on track with answers to their questions.
Interview Questions: Tell us about a time when you had to correct a mistake that someone else made.
